description: The Oregon Board of Forestry will hold its next regular business meeting at 8:30 a.m. on Wednesday, Jan. 4, 2012, in the Tillamook Room - Building C, 2600 State St., in Salem. The meeting is open to the public. The agenda can be found on the board's website, www.oregonforestry.gov.

metadata.attribution: Rod Nichols, Oregon Department of Forestry
